---
description: TypeScript and JSX conventions including React imports and TEXT_MANAGER access
globs: "**/*.tsx,**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Don't use React.* namespace (e.g. use `ReactElement` not `React.ReactElement`).
- TEXT_MANAGER: prefer direct access over destructuring for proper type checking.
- When the same text key is used in multiple places, consider a dedicated hook.
